{"word":"ἐπέοικα","slug":"ἐπέοικα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n38704\" key=\"e)pe/oika\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐπέοικα</orth>, <sense id=\"n38704.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be like, suit,</tr_> c. dat. pers., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὅς τις οἷ τ᾽ ἐπέοικε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:392\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.392</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: elsewh. impers., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">it is fit, proper,</tr_> c. dat. pers. et <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σφῶϊν μέν τ᾽ ἐπέοικε . . ἑστάμεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:341\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.341</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ϝέῳ δέ τε πάντ᾽ ἐπέοικε . . κεῖσθαι</foreign> '<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tis a seemly thing</tr_> for a young man to lie dead, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:71\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.71</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg003.perseus-grc1:7:95\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">N.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.95</biblScope> </bibl>: c. acc. pers. et <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λαοὺς δ᾽ οὐκ ἐπέοικε . . ταῦτ᾽ ἐπαγείρειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:126\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.126</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὅν τ᾽ ἐπέοικε βουλὰς βουλεύειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:146\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.146</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: with <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood> understood, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀποδάσσομαι ὅσσ᾽ ἐπέοικε [ἀποδάσασθαι]</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24:595\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.595</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὔτ᾽ οὖν ἐσθῆτος δευήσεαι οὔτε τευ ἄλλου, ὧν ἐπέοιχ᾽ ἱκέτην . . ἀντιάσαντα [μὴ δεύεσθαι]</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:6:193\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.193</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n38704.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ part.\">part.</a></mood> pl., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπεικότα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">seemly, fit,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τινί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg006.perseus-grc1:669\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ch.\">Ch.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">669</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href